title: Papyrus New Baby Card (Can't Wait)
description: Celebrate the new arrival with this adorable Baby Congrats card from Papyrus Featuring a happy little “cutie” orange, rendered in light, colorful brushstrokes against a light blue sky dotted with flowers, this design is asking to be “picked” A cheerful hand-lettered message on the inside lets the parent or couple know just how excited you are for them. Comes with a white envelope with gold inside flap, and gold foil seal.
